      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. can u give me a concrete example? like if we had 500k in cogs last year but we lost 50k to shrinkage, and our avg inventory was 100k, how does that change the ratio? also, do u have any ideas on why a sudden spike in shrinkage happens in most warehouses?",
