      "content": "that makes sense. the math is clear. but the \"why\" part is what's killing us. it's not just one thing, it's like... items are just disappearing from the middle of the aisles without any security footage picking up anything suspicious. it's almost like they're just vanishing into thin air. what are some other common causes for that kind of \"ghost\" shrinkage?",
